1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:07,440
Why so many lies? Say it… Say it, come on,
say it. Do not stay silent, say something.

2
00:00:08,440 --> 00:00:13,680
Look… You have no part in Murat’s, my
brother’s, my brother’s death, right Ateş?

3
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:15,960
I did not want him to die.

4
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:24,400
You, the man I loved, the man I
fell for, could not have done this.

5
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:28,760
Why are you with Tahir?

6
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:31,880
Why do you hate me and my family? Speak.

7
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:36,680
I am here to turn your life
into hell, Haydar Yıldırım.

8
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,720
So everything was your plan.

9
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:41,760
You are a menace.

10
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:44,680
How dare you enter my family?

11
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:50,240
I am not the Tahir you locked away.

12
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,560
What is your plan?

13
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,600
To kill me?

14
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,440
Death would be salvation for you.

15
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:57,880
What revenge is this?

16
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,120
What did we do?

17
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,480
Why the name Ateş?

18
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:02,640
Why 187 days of marriage?

19
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:08,080
187 days we were locked in basement.

20
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:13,360
Exactly 187 days.

21
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:17,720
Your father tortured us.

22
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:24,840
Just say the word. I will
make them all pay right now.

23
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:28,360
What are you saying, Nezir?
What do you think you are doing?

24
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:32,639
I would do anything for you.
To protect you. Because I…

25
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,640
Please.

26
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:38,520
If your love is as real
and as big as your revenge…

27
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,400
if you had to choose between them,

28
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:47,000
could you give up your
revenge for your love?

29
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:58,159
Love and revenge cannot stand side by
side. You either build, or you destroy.

30
00:02:58,160 --> 00:03:02,120
Decide who you want to be already.

31
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:14,240
If your love is real, kill
the revenge living inside you.

32
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:19,720
Because if you do not kill it, it will kill
everything beautiful, it will wipe everything out.

33
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:26,760
Are you able to do this?
Will you choose our love?

34
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:38,680
Which will you choose,
Ateş? Which one is your truth?

35
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:41,840
Our love, or your revenge? Say it.

36
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:49,600
After you fell into my heart, I asked
myself this question a thousand times.

37
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:55,080
I struggled a thousand
times to find a third way.

38
00:03:57,640 --> 00:04:05,480
This is such a war. No matter what I
choose, I am always the one who loses.

39
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,799
You could have come out of the darkness.

40
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,000
I come from that darkness, Mercan.

41
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:19,840
I am that darkness itself.

42
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:33,560
Maybe you need to change.
Maybe this is your last chance.

43
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:38,960
Look, I am here. I am not
leaving, I am still by your side.

44
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,920
Despite everything, I insist
for the sake of our love.

45
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:47,160
This is the only thing that
will make me believe you, Ateş.

46
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:52,920
Choosing us, choosing our love.

47
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:57,640
Making up for things? Some
things have no making up, Mercan.

48
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,080
Will my sister come back?

49
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:08,240
No, their voice is still here.

50
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:16,000
I wish, I wish I could turn back time.

51
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:21,440
Believe me, I would give my life for Eylül.

52
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,760
I would have died instead of her.

53
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:30,800
But it does not happen. Sadly,
it does not. It simply does not.

54
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:36,080
No matter what you do, no matter
what I do, we cannot change the past.

55
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,639
I am in pain too,

56
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:42,360
my childhood is dying together with yours.

57
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,800
Maybe it is time to let go, Ateş.

58
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:55,160
I am sure Eylül would want this too.

59
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:01,359
She would not want you to
waste yourself chasing revenge,

60
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:04,160
she would not want you to
ruin your life, everything.

61
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,240
Let us go now.

62
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,520
My son.
Yes, mother.

63
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,080
Who are you waiting for
at the window like this?

64
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:56,560
My beautiful one, I am
waiting for my bride, mother.

65
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,840
Zehra will arrive soon.

66
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,320
Beautiful, you say?

67
00:06:59,480 --> 00:06:59,840
Yes.

68
00:06:59,841 --> 00:07:01,400
This is the Zehra we know, right?

69
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:03,520
Yes, mother.

70
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,280
Beautiful beyond worlds.

71
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,040
Good. Let her come.

72
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,840
Look, she is coming
now. I will surprise her.

73
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,440
Now.

74
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,480
Surprise.

75
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,120
Welcome.

76
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,000
Thank you.

77
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,680
Come, Zehra, welcome.

78
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,280
Come, my wife, come.

79
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:38,519
Zehra my girl, since you are a bride now,

80
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:42,600
go make bride coffee so we can
drink it together, my son and I.

81
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,800
Right away, mother Binnaz.

82
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,800
Come on then.

83
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,280
Zehra, wait, something came to my mind.

84
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:56,040
I almost forgot.

85
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,600
I am craving stuffed vine leaves.

86
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,880
Olive oil stuffed leaves.

87
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:07,679
Now do this, make the coffees,

88
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,720
we drink them. Then make good
stuffed leaves for tonight,

89
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:14,680
nice and sour. We sit and eat together.

90
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:18,319
But listen, those rolls must be very thin,

91
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:20,000
as thick as my little finger.

92
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:23,280
If not, I will make you redo them
all from scratch, keep that in mind.

93
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,920
Stuffed leaves.

94
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:33,200
Mother Binnaz, are you
not exaggerating a bit?

95
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:37,920
I mean yes, you are testing
me, but this feels too much.

96
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:44,080
No dear, I need to test
the taste of your hands.

97
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,680
Go on, make the coffees.

98
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,480
Okay.

99
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:56,559
Zehra, oh look, I almost forgot again.

100
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:59,759
You make the coffee, let us do this,

101
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,480
we all drink our coffee together.

102
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:04,320
Before the stuffed
leaves, go to the mansion.

103
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:07,000
Change the sheets there, fix the pillows.

104
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:09,760
Do all of them neatly, properly.

105
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,440
Military order, perfect discipline.

106
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,840
I will come and inspect them.

107
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:15,600
After that, you go and
make the stuffed leaves.

108
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,200
Okay.

109
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:41,240
Mother, was this not too
heavy for the first day?

110
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:45,360
No dear, should we not drink
one coffee from our bride’s hand?

111
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,680
Being Binnaz’s bride is not easy.

112
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,440
So you say.

113
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,680
Then I will help too.

114
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,840
My wife.

115
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,480
Mercan.

116
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:47,400
She says choose your revenge, or choose us.

117
00:10:57,480 --> 00:11:01,960
Until now, my only
purpose in life was revenge.

118
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:11,880
Does a person give up their own
existence, their promise, for love?

119
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,640
Brother.

120
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,520
Look, love is like this.

121
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,160
Love makes a person do everything in life.

122
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,680
Sometimes a person gets
swept by love’s current,

123
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,040
and makes mistakes they should not.

124
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,400
It does not mean it
will always stay this way.

125
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:39,160
Maybe your love will make us do
the greatest right of our lives.

126
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,000
You are the most innocent in this story.

127
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,560
But you are also the
ones who suffer the most.

128
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:53,000
Is there no wrong in this at all?

129
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,960
The only innocent one is Mercan.

130
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,280
I dragged her into my own hell.

131
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,080
Now I watch her burn.

132
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,680
Have you ever thought about this?

133
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,920
Wondered if we took the wrong road?

134
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:24,000
When a person stays alone like this,
they start thinking and questioning.

135
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:32,760
Being tested from where
you feel safest hurts deeply.

136
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:40,840
Everything I hold slips away from my hands.

137
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,480
I found a way to make you forgive me.

138
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,239
I have great news for you.

139
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,240
Get out.

140
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:01,040
Okay, I will say one thing and leave.

141
00:13:01,680 --> 00:13:03,720
I found a clause in the contract.

142
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:07,640
You are able to remove
Nezir from the partnership.

143
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,520
Why was this not seen for so long?

144
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:13,800
Why did we endure this
man for so long then?

145
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,760
Because of the chaos.

146
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:18,600
My head was confused, I skipped it.

147
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,120
I am sorry.

148
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,240
Did you know?

149
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,320
I told him first when I noticed.

150
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,800
He asked me to tell you and resolve it.

151
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,960
Handle the rest with Cemal.

152
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:43,400
Check all contracts, see
if there is any other issue.

153
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:48,600
Especially those with Aslı’s signature.

154
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,200
I am doing it already.

155
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,120
I started long ago.

156
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:01,000
How do you lie like this,
looking us in the eye?

157
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,160
Maybe because I had no choice?

158
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,080
Let some time pass.

159
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:08,440
She will forgive anyway.

160
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,160
Listen to this talk.

161
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,800
Fine, trust is something
repaired over time.

162
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:19,080
But a lifetime will not
repair what you did, Aslı.

163
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:39,800
I offered him a way out, Demet.

164
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:44,880
If she reaches out, we might
have a chance, but still silence.

165
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:51,800
I still want to believe him.

166
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:56,080
But believing him means
turning my back on my family.

167
00:14:57,280 --> 00:14:58,840
It means ignoring his lies.

168
00:15:02,120 --> 00:15:03,160
What will I do?

169
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:06,960
First, you will stop
being so hard on yourself.

170
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:11,560
Wherever I turn, I sink into mud.

171
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:15,920
My family on one side, Ateş on the other.

172
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:18,280
Everything in my life is falling apart.

173
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:19,880
Everything.

174
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:23,359
Sometimes when everything
piles up like this,

175
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,520
you think life will always stay this way.

176
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,960
But the sun rises again every morning.

177
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:34,600
It feels as if it will never rise.

178
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:38,560
I feel as if I will
stay in darkness forever.

179
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,640
Anyway, I am hanging up now.

180
00:15:48,320 --> 00:15:49,320
See you.

181
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,880
We will talk, dear. I am kissing you.

182
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:18,160
This Ms. Müzeyyen piled all of this here.

183
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:22,359
Organic beans, organic lentils.

184
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,880
There is more there too, what is that?

185
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:26,200
Organic chickpeas, even green ones.

186
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:27,840
God forgive me.

187
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:30,000
If the woman did one good
deed, I would understand.

188
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:34,240
No, she will live longer and do more harm.

189
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:49,040
We need to name this
already, this cannot go on.

190
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,800
Should I kiss your hand, Aunt Binnaz?

191
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:58,280
Of course, let us name
it. Let it have a name.

192
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:04,480
Son, call your family
and tell them to come ask.

193
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,640
What happened, did something happen?

194
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,640
No, nothing happened, mother.

195
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,960
Nothing happened. What could happen?

196
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,040
We were surprised.

197
00:17:21,120 --> 00:17:22,800
Surprised, only surprised.

198
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,200
Wait.

199
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:29,360
We said something, do
not make a man regret it.

200
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:35,720
Anyway, talk to your family.

201
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,960
Let me know beforehand when they will come.

202
00:17:38,120 --> 00:17:39,120
Whenever they come.

203
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,920
So we prepare accordingly.

204
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:43,096
So we are not embarrassed
before the in laws.

205
00:17:43,120 --> 00:17:44,479
Let us prepare properly, alright?

206
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,480
Of course.

207
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:49,960
Çiçek.

208
00:17:51,120 --> 00:17:52,440
Make me some tea too, my girl.

209
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,680
The tea turned out great.

210
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:59,520
Of course, Çiçek’s tea is always good.

211
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:04,440
You still did not learn
how to throw properly.

212
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,240
It does not work.

213
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:29,200
Like this.

214
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,640
Stretch your arm well.

215
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:41,920
The stone should travel
parallel to the water.

216
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,440
Like this.

217
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,240
Tahir taught me this.

218
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:18,880
Looks like I did not teach well.

219
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:24,080
You made no progress since that day.

220
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,800
Was that a challenge?

221
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:29,120
Always.

222
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,720
Are you in?

223
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,880
Always.

224
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,920
Do not be upset when you lose.

225
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,840
I would never be upset losing to you.

226
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:55,200
But you will not win.

227
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,680
Go on, start.

228
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:51,320
You only have technique.

229
00:21:51,840 --> 00:21:53,280
No soul.

230
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:56,960
You do not win without soul.

231
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:24,280
Bravo.

232
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:25,800
You won.

233
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,200
You lost on purpose.

234
00:22:28,520 --> 00:22:29,880
Do not think I did not understand.

235
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:32,080
Then you misunderstood.

236
00:22:33,280 --> 00:22:34,600
I think I understood well.

237
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,880
You are only lucky today.

238
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:43,600
I will never be sure of that.

239
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:46,720
Like I am not sure of your love.

240
00:22:57,600 --> 00:23:01,800
My love is solid and real like this stone.

241
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,360
I want to believe you.

242
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,040
Please help me.

243
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:56,000
Because I cannot do this alone.

244
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:23,440
I cannot even help myself, Mercan.

245
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:33,280
I am full of regrets inside.

246
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:46,560
My Demet.

247
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:47,680
What did you do, brother?

248
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:48,960
Did you talk to Mercan?

249
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:50,640
She will look around a bit now, right?

250
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:54,319
I did not.

251
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:55,800
I did not talk.

252
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:57,400
I only gave morale.

253
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,240
And you call yourself a sister.

254
00:24:59,840 --> 00:25:01,920
She needs to get away from
that sly man called Ateş.

255
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:03,360
Someone here loves him.

256
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,880
I know, but it is unreturned love.

257
00:25:07,560 --> 00:25:08,680
Mercan is in love with Ateş.

258
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,120
There is nothing left between Burak and me.

259
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,856
Do not drag it out and strain people.

260
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,880
We are only friends.

261
00:25:29,960 --> 00:25:31,840
Let it be so then.

262
00:25:38,000 --> 00:25:39,000
Anyway.

263
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,560
Mr. Ateş has work.

264
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:42,560
Tomorrow’s meeting.

265
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:45,280
The company has some demands,
we need to handle them.

266
00:25:45,320 --> 00:25:46,760
I need to call Mr. Ateş.

267
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:49,000
His schedule is crowded lately.

268
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,520
I will tell him when I get home.

269
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:04,160
Who knows what nonsense is going
on in that flashy mansion again.

270
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:08,040
Good thing we are poor, but
the poor have different troubles.

271
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:18,840
Nothing we say pleases anyone.

272
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:21,440
Always attitude, always cold looks.

273
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,240
Good grief.

274
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:25,159
Who knows what problem this woman has.

275
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:28,120
If only she smiled once, always irritated.

276
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:37,520
My mother finally agreed.

277
00:26:37,760 --> 00:26:40,440
There is no obstacle left for us, Malik.

278
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:43,480
Well, there is one obstacle actually.

279
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:48,280
Do not upset Aunt Binnaz anymore, alright?

280
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:50,160
I do not want to lie to her anymore.

281
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:53,200
Honestly, I agree, let us not lie to her.

282
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:55,880
She will get furious this time.

283
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:59,120
When she gets stubborn, disaster.

284
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:02,240
Where we come from, they
call this the Black Sea vein.

285
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:03,440
It is fierce.

286
00:27:04,360 --> 00:27:05,400
Black Sea vein.

287
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:06,960
Fierce.

288
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:09,760
We need to do something about this now.

289
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,640
But what?

290
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:15,920
Look my love, we will
be more determined now.

291
00:27:16,680 --> 00:27:20,240
If we are determined, no
one will stand in our way.

292
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:29,040
Start looking at wedding dresses.

293
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:34,160
I planned my wedding dress
in my head since I was eight.

294
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,360
What kind?

295
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:37,960
Look now.

296
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:38,680
How?

297
00:27:38,681 --> 00:27:41,920
The neckline will be like this.

298
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:46,920
Puffy sleeves, lace and all.

299
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,640
Shiny.

300
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:51,520
I want it puffy like this.

301
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:54,480
But not overly plain either.

302
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:58,120
They like plain, but it feels empty.

303
00:27:58,600 --> 00:28:02,480
By puffy I do not mean too puffy.

304
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:07,200
I want a layered lace dress.

305
00:28:23,360 --> 00:28:25,040
Lace matters, you say.

306
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:27,560
Of course dear, I am a lace woman.

307
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:32,560
Did you think about after that, lace woman?

308
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:34,800
After?

309
00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:37,000
Yes, after marriage.

310
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:40,600
Like how it will be, how many children.

311
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:45,400
When I first saw you, I
thought about everything.

312
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:49,680
I will make you very happy.

313
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:54,080
By the way, devotion wins in our house.

314
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,000
Oh.

315
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:56,360
Yes.

316
00:28:56,720 --> 00:29:00,000
Stop saying that, you
will bring the evil eye.

317
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:03,800
I do not want big worlds.

318
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:07,280
One room is enough if we are together.

319
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:09,800
Then I would be the happiest woman alive.

320
00:29:11,120 --> 00:29:12,120
I love you.

321
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,120
Me too.

322
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,720
Children, I mean.

323
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,960
We will see.

324
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,920
We will see then.

325
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,160
Wait.

326
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:54,880
Do not bother trying to sway Ateş.

327
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:56,520
His side is clear.

328
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:03,919
If you use your femininity and slip
into his bed to pull him to your side

329
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:04,920
know your place.

330
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:08,680
You do not speak to me like this.

331
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:13,280
A woman speaking to another
woman like this is ugly.

332
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,160
Do not.

333
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:31,720
You go, I will handle it.

334
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:39,840
How do you do this?

335
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:41,679
How many times did I tell you?

336
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:45,760
How many more warnings do you need to
stay away from Mercan, Mother Müzeyyen?

337
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:51,120
If this revenge were only yours, you
would speak and I would stay silent.

338
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:54,360
You might have given up your revenge.

339
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:58,080
You might have left your
sister's blood on the ground.

340
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:03,640
I did not give up my revenge.

341
00:31:05,560 --> 00:31:06,960
Mercan is not your counterpart.

342
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:09,560
She has no guilt.

343
00:31:10,640 --> 00:31:13,600
The man called Haydar killed my husband.

344
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:15,560
My baby was stillborn from grief.

345
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:21,280
If my loved ones are under the ground,
they will be under the ground too.

346
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,560
With you, or despite you.

347
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:53,679
See?

348
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:58,800
She still walks around this house
shamelessly, as if nothing happened.

349
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:03,880
Dressed to the nines,
roaming outside for months.

350
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:08,640
God give everyone an enemy as soft as you.

351
00:32:13,600 --> 00:32:15,400
Do not belittle my pain, Mother Müzeyyen.

352
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,240
My hatred will not end.

353
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:28,280
Of course it will not.

354
00:32:29,320 --> 00:32:30,320
It will not end.

355
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:34,720
I will never allow it to end.

356
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:40,560
Cemal.

357
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,760
Yes, Mr. Haydar.

358
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:52,760
Sadly, we reached the end of
the time we allocated for you.

359
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:58,160
What is going on?

360
00:32:59,160 --> 00:33:00,160
What are you doing?

361
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,520
Let go.

362
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,000
Let go.

363
00:33:03,840 --> 00:33:04,840
Haydar.

364
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:07,120
You are going nowhere.

365
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,536
What are you doing? Where
are you taking my father?

366
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:10,680
Where he belongs.

367
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:13,040
He will answer for what he did.

368
00:33:19,280 --> 00:33:20,800
What will you do? Let him go.

369
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:22,400
Go to your room.

370
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,776
I will not go. I said let go.
I said go to your room.

371
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:25,160
Let go.

372
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,240
To your room.

373
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:30,160
Throw him in the basement.

374
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:31,880
Mercan.

375
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:34,240
Let go of him.

376
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:35,480
Let me go.

377
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,960
Ateş.

378
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:42,520
Let me go.

379
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:43,600
Do not follow me.

380
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,640
Let go of my arm.

381
00:33:45,080 --> 00:33:46,080
You cannot go.

382
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:50,400
What will you do in the basement?

383
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,600
Let go.

384
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:12,600
Let go.

385
00:34:12,601 --> 00:34:13,920
What are you doing?

386
00:34:17,640 --> 00:34:18,640
Let go.

387
00:34:24,640 --> 00:34:25,640
Let go.

388
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:28,640
Take his clothes off.

389
00:34:30,080 --> 00:34:31,080
Are you insane?

390
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,360
What are you doing?

391
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,960
Let go.

392
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,400
What is your aim, Ateş?

393
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:44,240
Out.

394
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:51,120
Cemal, you too.

395
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,480
Tahir.

396
00:35:02,560 --> 00:35:03,560
Tahir.

397
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:07,120
Müzeyyen uses you as a
weapon for her revenge.

398
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:09,840
I did not kill her
husband. I killed no one.

399
00:35:12,640 --> 00:35:13,640
Rıza did it.

400
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:15,080
Rıza planned everything.

401
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:18,200
Eylül.

402
00:35:18,680 --> 00:35:20,160
Eylül died from illness.

403
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,456
He killed your parents too.

404
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:23,920
Rıza did it.

405
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:25,200
Eylül died from illness.

406
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,680
He killed your parents too.

407
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,120
Rıza did it.

408
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,160
Rıza did it.

409
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:34,000
Brother, let me go, help me.

410
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,120
You will stay locked here.

411
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:02,080
Like the 187 days we stayed.

412
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:13,480
Like you imprisoned Eylül and me here.

413
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,280
No.

414
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,640
Look at these walls carefully.

415
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,960
We knew every inch of this place.

416
00:36:45,640 --> 00:36:47,360
You will learn too.

417
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:54,560
We heard voices at night.

418
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:58,640
Eylül would come hug me in fear.

419
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:01,880
I told her stories so she could sleep.

420
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:19,760
But these walls hold the
screams of two children.

421
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:46,840
If your love is real,
kill the revenge inside you.

422
00:37:47,240 --> 00:37:49,119
Because if you do not kill it,

423
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:51,880
it will kill everything beautiful,
it will wipe everything out.

424
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:54,000
Are you able to do this?

425
00:37:54,520 --> 00:37:55,760
Will you choose our love?

426
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:21,480
No.

427
00:38:21,960 --> 00:38:23,520
No, I will not stay here.

428
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:24,800
I cannot stay here.

429
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:26,240
Let me go.

430
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,040
Tahir, get me out of here.

431
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:29,760
Tahir.

432
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:30,480
Mercan.

433
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,440
My daughter Mercan.

434
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:33,800
Get me out of here, my daughter.

435
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,440
Open the door.

436
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:45,080
Get me out, I cannot stay here.

437
00:38:54,520 --> 00:38:55,759
Your pain is so great,

438
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:56,240
get me out.

439
00:38:56,241 --> 00:38:57,401
You are losing to your anger.

440
00:38:59,120 --> 00:39:00,920
Everyone must pay one day.

441
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:03,560
If there is guilt, it will be paid.

442
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:05,880
But not like this.

443
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:08,160
They answer before justice.

444
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:10,320
My daughter Mercan.

445
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:11,560
Get me out, my daughter.

446
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,960
How much guilt could there be anyway?

447
00:39:17,200 --> 00:39:18,800
Revenge became your greatest burden.

448
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:23,440
You punish yourself, not others.

449
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:29,560
Get me out, my daughter.

450
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:33,400
Open the door.

451
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:38,079
I cannot stay here, get me out.

452
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:40,240
Get me out. I cannot stay here, get me out.
Get me out.

453
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:43,160
Get me out.

454
00:39:45,560 --> 00:39:46,920
My daughter Mercan, get me out.

455
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:50,560
Leave us alone.

456
00:39:53,080 --> 00:39:54,200
Get me out.

457
00:40:21,720 --> 00:40:26,320
There is no sound of you here.

458
00:40:29,160 --> 00:40:33,160
I cannot face your image.

459
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:44,799
I lack the strength to bear your longing.

460
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:50,800
I have no strength, brother.

461
00:40:55,600 --> 00:41:02,800
My head weighs on the pillow,
sleep is forbidden to me.

462
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:10,960
My world is false, my world is false.

463
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:19,800
What should I do with feast water?

464
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:27,760
You are gone, brother, you are gone.

465
00:41:28,640 --> 00:41:36,640
You are gone, brother, you are gone.

466
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:14,760
I could not grasp this world’s desire.

467
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:23,120
No one heard my cry.

468
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:34,680
Will this heartache ease in the afterlife?

469
00:42:36,160 --> 00:42:38,800
Heartache.

470
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:47,800
What should I do with
feast and celebration?

471
00:42:49,120 --> 00:42:54,800
You are gone, brother, you are gone.

472
00:42:56,120 --> 00:43:04,120
You are gone, brother, you are gone.

473
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:35,040
What are you doing in my house?

474
00:43:37,120 --> 00:43:39,320
Exactly what I expected, Ateş Karahan.

475
00:43:41,120 --> 00:43:43,560
I knew there was something
behind this show from the start.

476
00:43:44,640 --> 00:43:46,080
You are not strong.

477
00:43:48,160 --> 00:43:50,640
You are pitiful, a two faced pitiful man.

478
00:43:53,200 --> 00:43:54,440
The day you waited for arrived.

479
00:43:56,520 --> 00:43:58,480
But the ending you expect will never come.

480
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:04,520
I see the games you
play to influence Mercan.

481
00:44:06,800 --> 00:44:09,480
You enter every path for a
woman who does not love you.

482
00:44:10,440 --> 00:44:13,600
That is the real pitiful
and two faced part.

483
00:44:16,520 --> 00:44:18,240
Show off all you want.

484
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:21,760
You lost Mercan forever by lying to her.

485
00:44:23,040 --> 00:44:24,240
She will never return to you.

486
00:44:25,760 --> 00:44:28,000
The one by her side
after you leave will be me.

487
00:44:31,880 --> 00:44:34,920
Rather than being a
beggar of love like you,

488
00:44:35,840 --> 00:44:37,840
I choose separation with dignity.

489
00:44:39,840 --> 00:44:41,120
Do not get excited.

490
00:44:42,800 --> 00:44:43,800
Sorry.

491
00:44:44,560 --> 00:44:46,440
You will be the one waiting at the door.

492
00:44:51,960 --> 00:44:52,960
Because she is mine.

493
00:44:58,560 --> 00:45:00,240
And if you get close to her,

494
00:45:00,960 --> 00:45:02,600
I will kill you.

495
00:45:04,040 --> 00:45:05,040
I will wait.

496
00:45:06,120 --> 00:45:09,000
Because Mercan will see the truth one day.

497
00:45:09,520 --> 00:45:10,520
I know.

498
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,800
Like I know you will leave.

499
00:45:14,920 --> 00:45:17,880
Your love is a lie, like your name.

500
00:45:20,400 --> 00:45:23,960
I am not leaving anywhere
until I take Mercan, Ateş Karahan.

501
00:45:26,120 --> 00:45:27,440
You missed something.

502
00:45:29,040 --> 00:45:30,240
You are in my mansion.

503
00:45:31,800 --> 00:45:33,840
And I am staying.

504
00:45:37,080 --> 00:45:38,360
You are leaving.

505
00:45:40,200 --> 00:45:41,200
Come on.

506
00:45:54,400 --> 00:45:58,240
So we will see Mr. Haydar
locked in the storage room too.

507
00:45:58,520 --> 00:45:59,600
What a world.

508
00:46:04,440 --> 00:46:06,880
You reap what you sow.

509
00:46:09,240 --> 00:46:10,480
Why would he do this?

510
00:46:13,400 --> 00:46:14,400
There is a reason.

511
00:46:14,760 --> 00:46:16,240
Do not interfere, son.

512
00:46:17,240 --> 00:46:18,680
That boy suffered a lot.

513
00:46:19,320 --> 00:46:20,320
Oh my child.

514
00:46:21,400 --> 00:46:25,880
Never belittle someone with love or pain.

515
00:46:28,640 --> 00:46:30,560
Is Mr. Haydar truly this bad?

516
00:46:30,920 --> 00:46:34,600
As bad as in the news?

517
00:46:35,960 --> 00:46:38,240
If Mr. Ateş says so, it is true.

518
00:46:39,120 --> 00:46:41,200
I have been with them
for long, he does not lie.

519
00:46:42,080 --> 00:46:44,000
Did they never mention this?

520
00:46:45,640 --> 00:46:47,240
Did you know?

521
00:46:48,920 --> 00:46:50,600
I said I did not hear.

522
00:46:51,560 --> 00:46:53,000
They never spoke near me.

523
00:46:57,400 --> 00:47:00,000
Do not involve yourselves.
This is not your matter.

524
00:47:03,320 --> 00:47:04,720
What happened happened to us.

525
00:47:09,160 --> 00:47:11,520
These ones came and stayed on our heads.

526
00:47:19,080 --> 00:47:22,320
Çiçek, speak properly
with your sister in law.

527
00:47:26,920 --> 00:47:30,840
As of today, she is my sister in law.

528
00:47:35,200 --> 00:47:36,920
Sister in law.

529
00:48:20,360 --> 00:48:21,360
Where are you going?

530
00:48:23,240 --> 00:48:24,800
To the guest room.

531
00:48:25,880 --> 00:48:27,400
I will leave the mansion if needed.

532
00:48:27,640 --> 00:48:30,360
I would stay on the street rather
than stay in the same room as you.

533
00:48:33,200 --> 00:48:36,160
No such thing. You are going nowhere.

534
00:48:36,400 --> 00:48:38,520
Let go of me. What will you do?

535
00:48:39,160 --> 00:48:40,640
Will you lock me in this room too?

536
00:48:41,520 --> 00:48:43,560
You are both savior and executioner.

537
00:48:45,840 --> 00:48:48,880
I will go if needed. You will stay here.

538
00:48:51,600 --> 00:48:54,480
Then go. Go.

539
00:48:58,160 --> 00:49:00,359
I asked you to choose.

540
00:49:00,360 --> 00:49:02,600
You chose revenge, not love.

541
00:49:03,840 --> 00:49:05,480
Since you are so sensitive about price,

542
00:49:06,080 --> 00:49:07,720
pay the price of your choices now.

543
00:49:08,600 --> 00:49:09,760
Leave. Leave.

544
00:49:10,000 --> 00:49:12,080
Leave my life, my mind, my heart.

545
00:49:14,520 --> 00:49:17,560
I will come back soon. Then we talk.

546
00:49:24,360 --> 00:49:25,640
What will I talk to you about?

547
00:50:05,360 --> 00:50:06,360
Cemal.

548
00:50:07,840 --> 00:50:09,800
Ateş still does not look at my face.

549
00:50:11,040 --> 00:50:12,400
I did what you said.

550
00:50:14,760 --> 00:50:16,800
This stays between us, right?

551
00:50:21,160 --> 00:50:23,120
Aslı, for God’s sake.

552
00:50:23,360 --> 00:50:24,920
What difference does it make?

553
00:50:26,080 --> 00:50:28,920
You will find another lie anyway.

554
00:50:32,000 --> 00:50:34,600
I cannot forget how you looked, Aslı.

555
00:50:36,120 --> 00:50:37,920
If I did not know, I
would have believed you.

556
00:50:40,400 --> 00:50:42,240
How did you lie so easily?

557
00:50:42,960 --> 00:50:45,200
Maybe you lied before too.

558
00:50:46,400 --> 00:50:48,680
Do not do this, Cemal.

559
00:50:49,840 --> 00:50:52,720
I think you are smart
enough to understand, Aslı.

560
00:50:54,000 --> 00:50:56,960
So start telling me every lie you told.

561
00:50:58,800 --> 00:50:59,839
One moment.

562
00:50:59,840 --> 00:51:02,360
Who are you to question me?

563
00:51:02,800 --> 00:51:03,800
What is this attitude?

564
00:51:05,320 --> 00:51:06,400
Ateş is my brother.

565
00:51:07,240 --> 00:51:09,320
Anyone who wrongs Ateş is my enemy.

566
00:51:10,600 --> 00:51:12,640
We did not turn from our path, Ateş did.

567
00:51:13,040 --> 00:51:14,840
Understand this.

568
00:51:15,000 --> 00:51:16,640
Ateş did not turn away.

569
00:51:17,120 --> 00:51:18,120
He only fell in love.

570
00:51:21,560 --> 00:51:23,400
He did not scheme behind backs like you.

571
00:51:24,120 --> 00:51:27,480
But you, even if you do not say it,

572
00:51:27,520 --> 00:51:29,519
I will learn every
scheme you ran, one by one.

573
00:51:29,520 --> 00:51:30,840
God is my witness.

574
00:51:42,760 --> 00:51:44,800
If you think I will
allow this, you are wrong.

575
00:51:55,080 --> 00:51:57,120
If you find me, then maybe we talk.

576
00:51:58,720 --> 00:51:59,800
I am leaving this place.

577
00:52:00,800 --> 00:52:02,160
I will be free of all of you.

578
00:52:02,960 --> 00:52:03,960
Everyone.

579
00:52:06,920 --> 00:52:07,920
Where are you going?

580
00:52:08,320 --> 00:52:10,800
Move, I am leaving, do not interfere.

581
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:13,040
I will interfere so much you go nowhere.

582
00:52:13,760 --> 00:52:15,079
You cannot stop me.

583
00:52:15,080 --> 00:52:16,960
Constant bullying.

584
00:52:17,400 --> 00:52:18,400
I am a bully, yes.

585
00:52:18,600 --> 00:52:19,840
Crazy, wild, all of it.

586
00:52:20,800 --> 00:52:21,800
Do not resist.

587
00:52:22,160 --> 00:52:25,800
Either you come quietly,
or I take you by other means.

588
00:52:26,560 --> 00:52:27,640
You know those ways well.

589
00:52:28,360 --> 00:52:30,360
As if forcing makes a difference.

590
00:52:32,920 --> 00:52:33,920
Stop complaining.

591
00:52:34,760 --> 00:52:36,160
I complain and I walk.

592
00:52:36,840 --> 00:52:37,840
Stop pulling me.

593
00:52:38,600 --> 00:52:39,600
Let go.

594
00:52:43,800 --> 00:52:45,240
Oh my God.

595
00:52:45,440 --> 00:52:46,200
Look at this beauty.

596
00:52:46,201 --> 00:52:48,080
God created it with care.

597
00:52:48,640 --> 00:52:50,600
Do not lean back too much, my wife.

598
00:52:51,920 --> 00:52:53,480
Stop, stop.

599
00:52:58,280 --> 00:52:59,440
Now lean.

600
00:53:00,400 --> 00:53:01,480
Is it not more comfortable?

601
00:53:01,920 --> 00:53:03,800
My beautiful wife. Let me kiss you.

602
00:53:03,920 --> 00:53:05,280
Stop it.

603
00:53:06,560 --> 00:53:07,560
What happened?

604
00:53:09,040 --> 00:53:10,040
What?

605
00:53:10,400 --> 00:53:12,200
Your family still does not want me.

606
00:53:12,880 --> 00:53:14,896
Even your mother made me
kiss her hand reluctantly.

607
00:53:14,920 --> 00:53:15,920
For show.

608
00:53:16,160 --> 00:53:17,600
My wife, how could that be?

609
00:53:18,760 --> 00:53:21,040
If my mother did not want
it, she would never allow it.

610
00:53:21,640 --> 00:53:22,920
I understand, Berat.

611
00:53:23,280 --> 00:53:24,600
She did not do it from the heart.

612
00:53:27,200 --> 00:53:31,560
If she accepted me, we would celebrate.

613
00:53:33,480 --> 00:53:35,680
We got married, did we commit a crime?

614
00:53:37,240 --> 00:53:38,720
Of course.

615
00:53:39,160 --> 00:53:40,680
I have no one.

616
00:53:41,320 --> 00:53:43,360
Everything is given to me reluctantly.

617
00:53:46,040 --> 00:53:49,040
My beautiful wife, you want a celebration?

618
00:53:51,320 --> 00:53:55,480
You want a celebration.
I am taking charge now.

619
00:53:56,080 --> 00:53:57,520
I will handle it, alright?

620
00:53:58,320 --> 00:53:59,320
Trust me.

621
00:54:01,840 --> 00:54:03,400
I left my phone here.

622
00:54:07,320 --> 00:54:08,320
Mother.

623
00:54:09,160 --> 00:54:10,160
How are you, mother?

624
00:54:11,560 --> 00:54:12,560
I am fine.

625
00:54:13,760 --> 00:54:16,480
We say, we got married.

626
00:54:18,160 --> 00:54:18,760
You know.

627
00:54:18,761 --> 00:54:20,760
In honor of our marriage,

628
00:54:21,720 --> 00:54:23,560
shall we have a celebration dinner?

629
00:54:24,840 --> 00:54:26,200
Celebration dinner?

630
00:54:27,520 --> 00:54:29,520
This mansion was shaken.

631
00:54:29,640 --> 00:54:30,720
No stone left on stone.

632
00:54:30,880 --> 00:54:32,640
And you seek celebration?

633
00:54:33,080 --> 00:54:34,080
What dinner?

634
00:54:34,360 --> 00:54:35,480
Let it be. I do not want it.

635
00:54:36,720 --> 00:54:40,040
Mother, we married, let us decide.

636
00:54:42,720 --> 00:54:46,680
Can we not sit and eat together once?

637
00:54:50,120 --> 00:54:51,240
Do it, mother.

638
00:54:51,600 --> 00:54:52,600
Do a kindness.

639
00:54:58,120 --> 00:54:59,120
Fine, alright.

640
00:54:59,200 --> 00:55:01,120
Since you want it, we eat.

641
00:55:02,240 --> 00:55:03,240
Let me kiss you.

642
00:55:04,120 --> 00:55:05,120
Come.

643
00:55:05,760 --> 00:55:06,960
My dear mother.

644
00:55:07,160 --> 00:55:09,360
I have work, I am leaving.

645
00:55:10,080 --> 00:55:10,720
Okay, mother.

646
00:55:10,880 --> 00:55:12,480
Do not linger too long.

647
00:55:13,160 --> 00:55:15,520
I have work too, I will leave now.

648
00:55:22,720 --> 00:55:24,600
See? I handled it quickly.

649
00:55:25,520 --> 00:55:26,520
Always smile like this.

650
00:55:27,600 --> 00:55:28,720
My beautiful wife.

651
00:55:28,960 --> 00:55:31,080
There is nothing I would not do for you.

652
00:55:32,080 --> 00:55:34,320
Write this big in your mind.

653
00:55:35,080 --> 00:55:36,640
Leave no space for small doubts.

654
00:55:38,280 --> 00:55:38,960
Alright?

655
00:55:39,240 --> 00:55:40,920
My beautiful wife.

656
00:55:44,920 --> 00:55:46,200
May I kiss you once?

657
00:55:48,040 --> 00:55:49,040
Okay.

658
00:55:54,320 --> 00:55:55,840
What are you doing?

659
00:55:56,400 --> 00:55:57,200
Give me the key.

660
00:55:57,280 --> 00:55:58,360
I am locking the door.

661
00:55:58,760 --> 00:56:00,120
You go nowhere without talking.

662
00:56:00,320 --> 00:56:02,160
If it ends, it ends where it began.

663
00:56:02,400 --> 00:56:04,440
Give the key. Open the door.

664
00:56:04,640 --> 00:56:05,760
I only want you to listen.

665
00:56:06,360 --> 00:56:07,360
Then I open it.

666
00:56:07,840 --> 00:56:09,040
There is nothing to listen to.

667
00:56:09,480 --> 00:56:11,280
I saw what I needed and got my answer.

668
00:56:11,760 --> 00:56:15,400
I cannot turn back from my promise.

669
00:56:16,200 --> 00:56:17,200
Do you understand?

670
00:56:17,320 --> 00:56:18,560
Then what are we talking about?

671
00:56:19,360 --> 00:56:21,160
I wish you happiness with your revenge.

672
00:56:21,520 --> 00:56:23,120
Open the door now.

673
00:56:23,800 --> 00:56:24,880
What are you doing? Let go.

674
00:56:25,080 --> 00:56:26,320
Talking is not required.

675
00:56:26,880 --> 00:56:28,080
We will stay here for a while.

676
00:56:28,760 --> 00:56:30,040
You know me, do not push.

677
00:56:31,200 --> 00:56:32,200
I know you.

678
00:56:34,720 --> 00:56:38,280
I do not even know what to call you.

679
00:56:39,520 --> 00:56:41,000
Tahir or Ateş.

680
00:56:42,800 --> 00:56:44,039
I do not know you at all.

681
00:56:44,040 --> 00:56:46,640
I do not even know who you are.

682
00:56:47,720 --> 00:56:49,120
You know me better than anyone.

683
00:56:50,040 --> 00:56:51,480
Because you know me with your heart.

684
00:56:52,560 --> 00:56:55,080
I am both Tahir and Ateş.

685
00:56:56,200 --> 00:56:58,920
One is my innocence, one my anger.

686
00:57:00,720 --> 00:57:02,440
First my parents’ betrayal.

687
00:57:03,640 --> 00:57:04,640
Now yours.

688
00:57:08,680 --> 00:57:10,520
None of you are real.

689
00:57:11,080 --> 00:57:13,240
None of you dare to be real.

690
00:57:13,880 --> 00:57:18,400
How do you breathe among these lies?

691
00:57:18,640 --> 00:57:22,240
I cannot anymore. I cannot breathe.

692
00:57:35,600 --> 00:57:36,600
Let go.

693
00:57:37,720 --> 00:57:38,720
Do not touch me.

694
00:57:39,720 --> 00:57:41,320
I only wanted this to end.

695
00:57:42,480 --> 00:57:44,359
I wanted you to choose us and end this war.

696
00:57:44,360 --> 00:57:47,400
I wanted deaths and fights to stop.

697
00:57:48,840 --> 00:57:50,480
I wanted no one to get hurt.

698
00:57:51,920 --> 00:57:54,680
I wanted us to return
to normal, even a little.

699
00:57:56,200 --> 00:57:59,960
Normal? Is there normal for us anymore?

700
00:58:03,080 --> 00:58:06,440
I do not know. I know nothing.

701
00:58:06,840 --> 00:58:09,080
I am crushed under what I thought I knew.

702
00:58:09,520 --> 00:58:13,840
I sank into your mud, struggling to escape.

703
00:58:14,360 --> 00:58:17,400
I reach for you, but
you do not hold my hand.

704
00:58:18,360 --> 00:58:21,960
Why do you do this to
me? Why make me live this?

705
00:58:25,560 --> 00:58:28,360
Why pull me into your limbo?

706
00:58:29,440 --> 00:58:33,240
Why say you loved me?
Why make my life harder?

707
00:59:13,760 --> 00:59:15,120
Yes, Saliha.

708
00:59:18,920 --> 00:59:21,920
You need many things lately.

709
00:59:25,000 --> 00:59:26,840
You always ask for something.

710
00:59:30,680 --> 00:59:32,000
I will try to handle it.

711
00:59:43,680 --> 00:59:46,240
You will answer for what you
did to my husband and family.

712
00:59:49,080 --> 00:59:50,960
How will that be?

713
00:59:52,640 --> 00:59:54,960
One day I will catch your weakness.

714
00:59:55,800 --> 00:59:59,080
Then I will be right beside you.

715
01:00:01,160 --> 01:00:02,840
You are shameless.

716
01:00:03,840 --> 01:00:06,080
What was done to my husband.

717
01:00:07,800 --> 01:00:09,800
What about what was done to my husband?

718
01:00:12,520 --> 01:00:16,360
If your husband were a real man,
he helped others more than you.

719
01:00:17,680 --> 01:00:19,240
You killed my baby.

720
01:00:20,240 --> 01:00:21,959
You had my son killed.

721
01:00:21,960 --> 01:00:24,800
My baby was innocent. Not a murderer.

722
01:00:26,160 --> 01:00:28,400
All children are
innocent for their mothers.

723
01:00:29,400 --> 01:00:33,000
He might have erred. But
death was not the price.

724
01:00:33,440 --> 01:00:34,600
You wanted blood.

725
01:00:37,040 --> 01:00:39,360
I came to collect payment.

726
01:00:40,360 --> 01:00:41,600
I will not leave without it.

727
01:00:42,720 --> 01:00:43,720
Do not leave then.

728
01:00:44,840 --> 01:00:46,520
I am not done with you either.

729
01:00:47,520 --> 01:00:52,520
You took your child’s
pain out on my entire family.

730
01:00:53,520 --> 01:00:54,520
You had Murat killed.

731
01:00:56,000 --> 01:00:58,280
But I will not be as merciless as you.

732
01:00:59,840 --> 01:01:01,880
I will hold only you accountable.

733
01:01:02,800 --> 01:01:05,360
Only you will pay. Alone.

734
01:01:21,040 --> 01:01:22,400
Well, well.

735
01:01:23,360 --> 01:01:26,959
Well, well, well.

736
01:01:26,960 --> 01:01:27,960
Well done, girl.

737
01:01:28,640 --> 01:01:32,400
Sister, you make fried beans tonight.

738
01:01:32,840 --> 01:01:33,880
It suits it.

739
01:01:34,240 --> 01:01:38,360
No, I am making pickles.
Do not hit it again.

740
01:01:39,000 --> 01:01:40,000
Pickles.

741
01:01:40,720 --> 01:01:43,320
Surprise me once.

742
01:01:44,000 --> 01:01:46,160
Do something nice.

743
01:01:47,680 --> 01:01:50,640
Brother, you surprise us enough already.

744
01:01:50,760 --> 01:01:51,760
I am not needed.

745
01:01:55,560 --> 01:01:58,960
Çiçek, you are straight, plain straight.

746
01:02:00,520 --> 01:02:03,920
I prefer being straight over wavy like you.

747
01:02:04,720 --> 01:02:08,000
I cannot argue now and spoil my mood.

748
01:02:09,160 --> 01:02:11,480
I have a wedding dinner tonight.

749
01:02:11,960 --> 01:02:13,000
I invited Malik too.

750
01:02:15,520 --> 01:02:17,960
Malik? What does Malik
have to do with this?

751
01:02:18,960 --> 01:02:22,720
Not family, nothing.
Why is he at the dinner?

752
01:02:22,840 --> 01:02:24,800
You married a girl of two days.

753
01:02:26,640 --> 01:02:29,920
At least Zehra is known.

754
01:02:30,800 --> 01:02:32,760
Zehra is not known either, brother.

755
01:02:32,800 --> 01:02:33,800
It has been two days.

756
01:02:34,600 --> 01:02:35,600
Good grief.

757
01:02:36,320 --> 01:02:37,920
You talk too much.

758
01:02:38,120 --> 01:02:39,160
Am I wrong?

759
01:02:41,880 --> 01:02:43,360
What is going on here again?

760
01:02:44,200 --> 01:02:46,040
Nothing, mother.

761
01:02:46,320 --> 01:02:47,640
I watched a film.

762
01:02:47,960 --> 01:02:49,600
I was telling it to Çiçek.

763
01:02:51,160 --> 01:02:53,080
It was boring.

764
01:02:53,720 --> 01:02:56,280
I think the girl deceives the boy.

765
01:02:59,440 --> 01:03:01,880
You watched a film and discuss it.

766
01:03:02,160 --> 01:03:03,160
Yes, mother.

767
01:03:03,480 --> 01:03:06,120
Everything ended and you discuss films.

768
01:03:09,840 --> 01:03:12,440
Well done, my children.

769
01:03:12,640 --> 01:03:14,120
You will be film critics now.

770
01:03:27,600 --> 01:03:30,680
May I leave this room? I am bored.

771
01:03:33,440 --> 01:03:34,440
You cannot.

772
01:03:35,560 --> 01:03:35,880
Okay.

773
01:03:36,560 --> 01:03:38,240
Say it then.

774
01:03:39,360 --> 01:03:40,360
Tell me.

775
01:03:40,440 --> 01:03:41,880
Tell me how you deceived me.

776
01:03:44,320 --> 01:03:45,320
I did not deceive.

777
01:03:46,160 --> 01:03:47,600
I fell into love.

778
01:03:48,600 --> 01:03:50,160
Do you think I did not ask myself?

779
01:03:51,880 --> 01:03:53,680
Some questions have no answers.

780
01:03:54,840 --> 01:03:57,000
If you manage to be honest with yourself,

781
01:03:57,520 --> 01:04:00,040
every question has an answer.

782
01:04:01,800 --> 01:04:03,000
You do not understand, do you?

783
01:04:03,720 --> 01:04:05,760
I could not risk losing you.

784
01:04:06,240 --> 01:04:07,960
I went back and forth in this conflict.

785
01:04:09,680 --> 01:04:10,720
I gave up neither you,

786
01:04:13,160 --> 01:04:14,160
nor my revenge.

787
01:04:16,280 --> 01:04:17,280
Fine.

788
01:04:17,720 --> 01:04:21,720
Since revenge is so precious,
live with it, die with it.

789
01:04:22,400 --> 01:04:23,656
We talked about this, let us not drag it.

790
01:04:23,680 --> 01:04:26,760
Revenge is my entire life.

791
01:04:28,800 --> 01:04:29,800
This will not work.

792
01:04:30,800 --> 01:04:33,160
I will not watch you
harm yourself or others.

793
01:04:34,480 --> 01:04:35,480
Give me the key.

794
01:04:35,960 --> 01:04:36,960
I said give it.

795
01:04:38,080 --> 01:04:39,080
Open the door.

796
01:04:39,800 --> 01:04:41,920
I will not. Do you know why?

797
01:04:43,120 --> 01:04:44,440
There is still love in your eyes.

798
01:04:45,680 --> 01:04:46,680
Hatred too.

799
01:04:47,000 --> 01:04:49,160
No, I see it.

800
01:04:50,160 --> 01:04:51,520
Do not be so sure of yourself.

801
01:04:53,480 --> 01:04:55,040
I am sure.

802
01:04:59,800 --> 01:05:02,360
I thought this love would save
me from the darkness I fell into.

803
01:05:03,840 --> 01:05:06,600
Turns out I moved from
one darkness into another.

804
01:05:07,400 --> 01:05:09,400
From my family’s lies into yours.

805
01:05:12,720 --> 01:05:14,880
No more lies between us. Trust me.

806
01:05:15,760 --> 01:05:18,000
Too late. Let go.

807
01:05:18,440 --> 01:05:20,720
I will not. I will not give up on you.

808
01:05:21,000 --> 01:05:23,439
I said let go. You are too late.

809
01:05:23,440 --> 01:05:24,640
I will not allow you to leave.

810
01:05:24,760 --> 01:05:26,760
You are too late. Let go.

811
01:05:26,920 --> 01:05:28,200
I will not let go.
I said let go.

812
01:05:28,480 --> 01:05:28,920
I will not.

813
01:05:29,080 --> 01:05:30,320
This game is tiring, stop.

814
01:05:33,440 --> 01:05:35,176
I will not allow you
to leave. Did you hear?

815
01:05:35,200 --> 01:05:36,160
I will not lose to you.

816
01:05:36,161 --> 01:05:38,360
I will never allow you
to use my feelings again.

817
01:05:38,480 --> 01:05:39,200
I said let go of me.

818
01:05:39,400 --> 01:05:40,680
Enough, let go now.

819
01:05:56,680 --> 01:05:59,400
You stained the purest feeling I had.

820
01:06:00,200 --> 01:06:01,200
My love.

821
01:06:05,880 --> 01:06:08,760
Open the door now or I
will hit you. Did you hear?

822
01:06:58,600 --> 01:07:00,080
Oh, perfect.

823
01:07:02,440 --> 01:07:03,640
Well done, my girl.

824
01:07:06,800 --> 01:07:07,800
Let us see.

825
01:07:12,040 --> 01:07:14,320
Wow, wow.

826
01:07:16,040 --> 01:07:17,040
Look at this table.

827
01:07:18,400 --> 01:07:20,160
A real wedding table.

828
01:07:21,240 --> 01:07:23,880
You Black Sea women outdid yourselves.

829
01:07:24,720 --> 01:07:26,840
Mashallah. Everything ready?

830
01:07:27,160 --> 01:07:29,160
Ready, son. Sit down.

831
01:07:30,280 --> 01:07:32,400
Looks great. Bless your hands.

832
01:07:32,880 --> 01:07:35,360
A ready table looks great, right Zehra?

833
01:07:35,920 --> 01:07:38,960
You should have helped too, Zehra.

834
01:07:41,560 --> 01:07:42,560
Çiçek.
Çiçek.

835
01:07:42,880 --> 01:07:45,240
Brother, okay, Zehra will do it one day.

836
01:07:47,200 --> 01:07:49,120
She will cook, we eat.

837
01:07:49,680 --> 01:07:50,680
Right, my wife?

838
01:07:51,200 --> 01:07:52,240
Yes, my husband.

839
01:07:53,280 --> 01:07:54,920
She will. She is a guest today.

840
01:07:55,040 --> 01:07:55,360
Yes.

841
01:07:55,560 --> 01:07:56,560
Come on.

842
01:08:00,360 --> 01:08:02,279
Mother, since this is a special day,

843
01:08:02,280 --> 01:08:04,480
I want to make a speech.

844
01:08:05,120 --> 01:08:06,120
Go on.

845
01:08:12,760 --> 01:08:13,760
Mother.

846
01:08:14,360 --> 01:08:16,960
You chased after me so
much when I was little.

847
01:08:18,840 --> 01:08:21,919
I was a small anchovy, now a big bluefish.

848
01:08:21,920 --> 01:08:23,720
Your effort cannot be repaid.

849
01:08:24,560 --> 01:08:26,160
Even anchovy becomes bluefish.

850
01:08:29,320 --> 01:08:30,320
My sister.

851
01:08:30,400 --> 01:08:31,400
Çiçek.

852
01:08:31,760 --> 01:08:33,360
My fragrant sister.

853
01:08:34,040 --> 01:08:35,040
My dear.

854
01:08:35,560 --> 01:08:38,920
I used to hide your toys.

855
01:08:40,200 --> 01:08:42,800
When you found them later,
you came to play with me.

856
01:08:43,960 --> 01:08:48,159
I do not know if you were naive or kind,

857
01:08:48,160 --> 01:08:49,999
but you were kind.

858
01:08:50,000 --> 01:08:53,440
You are on the list of
debts that cannot be repaid.

859
01:08:55,240 --> 01:08:56,360
My brother’s rose.

860
01:08:56,720 --> 01:08:57,720
My dear.

861
01:08:59,000 --> 01:09:00,000
Then let us come to

862
01:09:00,760 --> 01:09:02,000
my wife.

863
01:09:07,960 --> 01:09:08,960
My wife.

864
01:09:11,360 --> 01:09:13,640
Since the moment I first saw you,

865
01:09:15,840 --> 01:09:16,880
I love you deeply.

866
01:09:17,960 --> 01:09:18,960
Oh.

867
01:09:21,680 --> 01:09:26,360
When you came to this
mansion, my heart opened.

868
01:09:29,880 --> 01:09:31,240
I am glad you came.

869
01:09:35,000 --> 01:09:36,800
To my home, my life.

870
01:09:44,000 --> 01:09:45,480
What a beautiful family we became.

871
01:09:46,880 --> 01:09:47,880
Right, mother?

872
01:09:49,040 --> 01:09:51,240
I suppose so, we will see.

873
01:09:58,000 --> 01:09:59,040
Indeed.

874
01:09:59,720 --> 01:10:01,200
Wait, wait.

875
01:10:02,480 --> 01:10:03,720
Who invited you?

876
01:10:06,800 --> 01:10:08,600
Çiçek did, Berat.

877
01:10:09,800 --> 01:10:11,240
No such thing. Come on.

878
01:10:11,600 --> 01:10:14,320
Mother, there is no ring, no engagement.

879
01:10:14,440 --> 01:10:15,840
What is this, sitting at the table?

880
01:10:16,400 --> 01:10:17,400
Get out.

881
01:10:19,040 --> 01:10:20,040
What?

882
01:10:20,560 --> 01:10:21,560
Come on.

883
01:10:21,720 --> 01:10:22,720
Berat, are you okay?

884
01:10:24,400 --> 01:10:25,000
We talked, remember?

885
01:10:25,001 --> 01:10:27,120
I came and congratulated you.

886
01:10:27,640 --> 01:10:28,640
Remember.

887
01:10:28,840 --> 01:10:29,840
I remember.

888
01:10:31,880 --> 01:10:33,360
But get out.

889
01:10:33,720 --> 01:10:34,880
Come on, it got cold.

890
01:10:35,680 --> 01:10:36,680
Brother.

891
01:10:43,560 --> 01:10:45,120
Okay, I joked.

892
01:10:45,200 --> 01:10:45,920
I joked.

893
01:10:46,120 --> 01:10:47,280
I would drag it out but fine.

894
01:10:47,480 --> 01:10:48,760
Oh Berat.
Are the flowers for me?

895
01:10:49,040 --> 01:10:50,320
Of course not.

896
01:10:50,680 --> 01:10:51,360
Oh my God.

897
01:10:51,640 --> 01:10:53,096
The flowers are for
the elder of our family.

898
01:10:53,120 --> 01:10:54,120
For Aunt Binnaz.

899
01:10:54,240 --> 01:10:55,416
Fine then.
Let me present them.

900
01:10:55,440 --> 01:10:57,039
You went through trouble, son.

901
01:10:57,040 --> 01:10:58,439
What trouble?

902
01:10:58,440 --> 01:11:01,040
See, thoughtful boy.

903
01:11:01,360 --> 01:11:03,400
Çiçek, take these and put them in a vase.

904
01:11:03,600 --> 01:11:04,120
Come on.

905
01:11:04,440 --> 01:11:05,440
Thank you, my child.

906
01:11:05,720 --> 01:11:06,080
You are welcome.

907
01:11:06,360 --> 01:11:07,360
I will just...
Sit here.

908
01:11:08,320 --> 01:11:09,040
Sit.

909
01:11:09,240 --> 01:11:10,240
Sit, my boy.

910
01:11:12,760 --> 01:11:13,760
Well.

911
01:11:16,760 --> 01:11:17,840
Open the door.

912
01:11:18,720 --> 01:11:21,160
Do not force me to do things I do not want.

913
01:11:27,160 --> 01:11:28,720
First, your finger touches the trigger.

914
01:11:28,920 --> 01:11:30,160
You take off the safety.

915
01:11:31,160 --> 01:11:33,040
Then you pull the trigger.

916
01:11:36,640 --> 01:11:38,600
Good that I taught you to use a gun.

917
01:11:45,040 --> 01:11:46,640
The first shot was meant for me.

918
01:11:49,880 --> 01:11:50,880
Shoot.

919
01:11:53,480 --> 01:11:56,560
Leaving or shooting
makes no difference now.

920
01:11:58,800 --> 01:11:59,800
Shoot.

921
01:12:05,760 --> 01:12:08,760
I taught you after all.

922
01:12:09,240 --> 01:12:10,960
Still, let me help.

923
01:12:23,640 --> 01:12:25,240
Do you think I live without you?

924
01:12:30,600 --> 01:12:33,040
Do you see what you turned me into?

925
01:12:34,000 --> 01:12:36,360
You ruined everything.

926
01:12:39,640 --> 01:12:40,840
For revenge.

927
01:12:41,760 --> 01:12:42,760
Am I guilty?

928
01:12:43,400 --> 01:12:45,080
Did I hurt you?

929
01:12:51,240 --> 01:12:53,760
Then why do you hurt me?

930
01:12:56,800 --> 01:12:59,360
I entered this mansion with rage.

931
01:12:59,720 --> 01:13:01,360
With great anger inside.

932
01:13:02,360 --> 01:13:03,600
Then you entered my world.

933
01:13:06,480 --> 01:13:07,840
You changed me.

934
01:13:08,880 --> 01:13:11,000
My feelings, my view, my inside changed.

935
01:13:12,560 --> 01:13:13,960
You became my entire life.

936
01:13:14,480 --> 01:13:15,560
What do you not understand?

937
01:13:19,320 --> 01:13:21,839
A blow from others fades,

938
01:13:21,840 --> 01:13:26,600
but one from the loved one kills.

939
01:13:28,360 --> 01:13:29,360
You killed me.

940
01:13:31,360 --> 01:13:34,440
Right when I began believing in life again,

941
01:13:36,440 --> 01:13:39,520
embracing love, at my happiest moment.

942
01:13:41,800 --> 01:13:43,920
Now I will kill you inside me.

943
01:13:51,720 --> 01:13:53,680
I am saying this one last time.

944
01:13:54,080 --> 01:13:55,080
Open the door.

945
01:13:55,720 --> 01:13:56,720
I will not.

946
01:13:57,240 --> 01:13:59,600
Until you believe in my
love, this door stays closed.

947
01:14:00,760 --> 01:14:02,040
If you do not believe, shoot me.

948
01:14:03,200 --> 01:14:04,600
Stop lying.

949
01:14:04,960 --> 01:14:05,880
I said open the door.

950
01:14:05,881 --> 01:14:07,441
This is not a lie, Mercan, you know it.

951
01:14:07,640 --> 01:14:08,120
No.

952
01:14:08,640 --> 01:14:09,240
Then shoot.

953
01:14:09,560 --> 01:14:10,840
Leave me alone, stay away.

954
01:14:11,080 --> 01:14:12,479
Mercan, listen to me.

955
01:14:12,480 --> 01:14:14,000
Do not. No, be silent.
